import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; @Component({ selector: 'app-panorama', templateUrl: './panorama.component.html', styleUrls: ['./panorama.component.scss'] }) export class PanoramaComponent implements OnInit { panoramaData: any; displayedColumns: string[] = ['id']; // Add other column names constructor(private http: HttpClient) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.fetchPanoramaData(); } fetchPanoramaData() { this.http.get('http://localhost:8000/api/v1/panorama').subscribe( (data: any) => { this.panoramaData = data; }, (error) => { console.error('Error fetching Panorama data:', error); } ); } }
